{"tid":650116,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局文件「粵語非母語」　Ben Sir ：粵語係我哋嘅母語　質疑教局壓抑粵語","createTime":"2018-05-02T05:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T03:10:26.000Z","uid":141060,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6e3e95f1e15236093bd542ee31ed2ba3a1bf88","tid":650116,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T05:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/130333_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F130333_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d33189dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源：歐陽偉豪 facebook 片段截圖、中大圖片<br />\n<br />\n早前有網民留意到，教育局曾向全港中小學派發多份普通話課程配套資料，當中一篇文章引用中大普通話中心學者指「香港漢族人的母語是漢語」，粵語只是「地域變體」的方言，普通話才是「正規的語言教育」。中大中文系前高級講師歐陽偉豪博士（Ben Sir）今天在Facebook狠批，質疑當局偏頗地引用「學術權威」；並指「粵語係我哋嘅母語」。<br />\n歐陽偉豪指，自己並非針對該文作者宋欣橋教授，而是「只想針對教育局引用權威的工夫及其背後的動機」。歐陽偉豪翻查中大網頁及宋欣橋履歷，其著作全是普通話著作，沒有一篇研究粵語；但教局卻引用一位沒有研究粵語的學者指「粵語不是香港人的母語」，質疑「教育局居然重視此觀點並將之傳給大眾」的用心。<br />\n歐陽偉豪表示，粵語為母語的香港學者多的是，「偏偏教育局在某普通話中心找來一位沒有粵語研究的內地學者替代粵語研究豐碩的香港學者，來為粵語是否母語作解說。」質疑該引用權威未夠精準。"},{"pid":"759a7107a53d05c0e8f347e0c1b3bd8dde501690","tid":650116,"uid":51529,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"母語既意思唔係母親育兒教既語言咩"},{"pid":"ef46591b052ed6db5e78bad3ef26e9db6ef68fc1","tid":650116,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T09:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/02/171625_b76273711411e91747c814a855e288d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2F171625_b76273711411e91747c814a855e288d7.png&h=937df08c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ceb7c5dfb5f8a237e1797c951e7f1f79d28a3645","tid":650116,"uid":15481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T09:17:32.000Z","msg":"地域變體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係都係普通話先係方言啦<br />\n九聲變四聲喎"},{"pid":"88683b51714c33bae64dc6d966d6cade6a5c882c","tid":650116,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T09:19:11.000Z","msg":"我唔撚識講母語咁仲算唔算母語？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9023f2e7394f49837546bc08a7150d16d8d97102","tid":650116,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 弱西智政府"},{"pid":"fe313acea2c05b8634c2b2ecbd0e4f58e23d3f9f","tid":650116,"uid":30782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9023f2e7394f49837546bc08a7150d16d8d97102","tid":650116,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 弱西智政府"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"比班撚屌管香港，香港點會唔退步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}